--- Switchblade / Soundwave ---

Switchblade turns around, and hops into a chair. He salutes lazily, 
and starts to explain, "Lord Megs, I, your loyal servant, witnessed 
Motormaster stab the console with his blade, and I cannot for the 
fuel of figure out why." he finishes smugly.

----------------------------

Soundave nods to Havotron. "When do we leave?"
